{"tid":1419782,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"美國將中國列為匯率操縱國　人民幣匯價急跌","createTime":"2019-08-06T02:35:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T03:02:39.000Z","uid":290687,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"404cdb6562a96bf27c41c3baacd33e7559f62a8e","tid":1419782,"uid":290687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T02:35:55.000Z","msg":"美國將中國列為匯率操縱國，是1994年後首次。離岸人民幣隨即下跌，較早時跌至7.136元人民幣兌1美元，創10年新低。<br />\n<br />\n美國財長發表聲明，美國政府確認中國正在操縱人民幣匯率，將與國際貨幣基金組織合作，消除來自中國的不公平競爭。<br />\n<br />\n人民幣匯價周一跌穿7算。人民銀行發表聲明，表示針對市場可能出現的正反饋行為，將繼續採取必要同有針對性措施。美國財政部認為，聲明等於公開承認具有操縱匯率的豐富經驗，並準備繼續採取這種操作。<br />\n<br />\n根據美國法律，要判定主要貿易夥伴是否操縱匯率有3個標準，包括有關經濟體的全球經常帳順差、對美國巨額貿易順差，以及持續單向干預匯市。而對於被列為匯率操縱國的經濟體，美國財政部會要求進行專門談判，目的為矯正被低估的貨幣匯價，並作出處罰，例如禁止參與美國政府採購合約。<br />\n<br />\n-RTHK<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1472968-20190806.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1472968-20190806.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=UMlFbumbAr%2BzuUpIk3BrKQ9axkDoCoA19ZsVt7gViHY%3D&h=6ec38a5d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1472968-20190806.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=1e1944d5\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1472968-20190806.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n跌啦跌啦 今鋪仲唔係辛辛苦苦20年 一把回到解放前<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50f5b097c0735b494fc73087f25cdbb102f267f2","tid":1419782,"uid":41545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03:01:10.000Z","msg":"口交部可以點應<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40e242792fb05a717c46f5be4f2e20ccabf1ecda","tid":1419782,"uid":10176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"50f5b097c0735b494fc73087f25cdbb102f267f2","tid":1419782,"uid":41545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03:01:10.000Z","msg":"口交部可以點應<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T03:02:39.000Z","msg":"反對外國勢力干預人民幣<br />\n對美國行為作出強烈譴責"}]}